== Romanian ==
===Adverb===
'''oare'''
#An interrogative. Rough English equivalent being "can", but ''oare'' has other usages beyond this.
=== Etymology ===
Disputed. The [[W:Romanian Academy|Romanian Academy]] derives it with some room for other possibilities from Latin ''[[volet]]'' [http://dexonline.ro/search.php?cuv=oare&source= ]. Other linguists hypothesize a substratum origin, pointing to an Albanian equivalent, ''[[vallë]]''.

